    "causal_summary": "The finished 20-iteration research in `research/research.md` locked the migration strategy that this packet now records as shipped. The delivered implementation migrated `@spec-kit/shared` and `@spec-kit/mcp-server` to native ESM, kept `@spec-kit/scripts` as CommonJS, and used explicit package-boundary async loading plus scripts-owned bridge code where CommonJS had to cross into ESM. Dual-build or conditional exports remained a fallback option only and were not needed for the shipped path.",
